International Food Policy Research Institute, ‘Implementing physical and virtual food reserves to protect the poor and prevent market failure’, February 2009<br />

<a href="http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/bp010.pdf" target="_self">http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/bp010.pdf</a><br />
Torero, M. (IFPRI), and J. von Braun (University of Bonn), ‘Alternative mechanisms to reduce food price volatility and price spikes’, 2009<br />

<a href="http://www.agritrade.org/events/documents/ToreroandvonBraun.pdf" target="_self">http://www.agritrade.org/events/documents/ToreroandvonBraun.pdf</a>&nbsp;<br />
